## 6. Logout Flow

*   **Triggers:** User clicks *"Logout"* button inside navigation bars.
*   **Operations:**
    *   Remove `token`, `user`, and `role` entries from `localStorage`.
    *   Set `currentUser` to `null` and `isAuthenticated` to `false` in `AuthContext`.
    *   Force a page redirection to the public landing page `/`.

---

## 7. Integration Summary with the backend Auth Module

| Page | Trigger Actions | Backend Route Called | Payload | Expected Response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `/auth/login` | Click "Get OTP" | `POST /api/v1/auth/send-otp` | `{ mobile }` | `{ success: true, message: "..." }` |
| `/auth/verify` | Submit OTP | `POST /api/v1/auth/verify-otp` | `{ mobile, otp }` | `{ token, user, role }` or `{ newCustomer: true }` |
| `/auth/register-customer` | Submit profile name | `POST /api/v1/auth/verify-otp` | `{ mobile, otp, name }` | `{ token, user, role }` |
| `/auth/register-worker` | Submit multi-step form | `POST /api/v1/auth/register/worker` | Multi-field JSON or multipart form | `{ token, worker, role }` |
